ZAbbrev (C port)
================

This repository contains a C implementation of ZAbbrev, a utility for 
deriving text abbreviations used by the Z-machine. It is based on the 
original C# version written by Henrik Åsman, which can be found at
<https://github.com/heasm66/zabbrev>. The C port was created and is
maintained by Jason Self.

