Requirements
------------

Building the program requires a standard C toolchain and the GNU 
Autotools. The following tools must be available:

* gcc or another ISO C compiler
* autoconf and automake
* make and a POSIX shell

No additional libraries are needed.

Building
--------

Run the following commands in the top-level directory:

autoreconf -i
./configure
make
make install # optional, install the program

Documentation
-------------

A Texinfo manual (doc/zabbrev.texi) and a manual page
(doc/zabbrev.1) are provided. Use make info or make html to build
the documentation in various formats.

Resources
---------

Report bugs to: j@jxself.org
zabbrev home page: https://jxself.org/git/?p=zabbrev.git

